.SS "Action Routines"
The SgIconGadget action routines are described below:
.IP "\fBHelp()\fP:"
Calls the callbacks for \fBXmNHelpCallback\fP if any exist.  If there are
no help callbacks for this widget, this action calls the help callbacks for
the nearest ancestor that has them.
